  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this trial was to compare two different uterotomy surgical techniques on the
      occurrence of a uterine niche and the risk of a number of short- and long-term gynecological
      complications associated with the presence and size of the niche.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
